Valid test cases:

1. Login using a valid phone number and password

2. Login using a valid email and password

3. Login using an valid phone number and password [with country code number +381]

4. Login using an valid phone number and password [with country code number 00381]

5. Login using an valid phone number and password [without country code number 065]

6. Verify clicking on eye icon to show password


Invalid test cases:

1. Login leaving a phone number or email field empty

2. Login leaving a password field empty

3. Login while using an invalid phone number or email [which are not registrated]

4. Login while using an invalid password

5. Login while making a spelling mistake on email [abc@gamil.com]

6. Verify login 10 times using an invalid passwords

7. Login using an old password after changing to the new one
